"ngram\": \"a confidence booster\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having (my teammates) there to lean on was absolutely amazing and I would not have made it through without them,\\\" Lee told Reuters.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.534258549295942, \"rank\": 0.4898349995555318, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 1580, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999969611508, \"rank\": 3.0196445354394924e-09, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my teammates\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But more than a support role for her teammates, Biles hopes to inspire young gymnasts, athletes and even adults to gain confidence and trust in themselves and learn how to handle tough times.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a support role\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"her teammates\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1636}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"young gymnasts\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"even adults\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"trust\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"tough times\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Never give up, there is light at the end of the tunnel.\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\